"690","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"691","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"692","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum investment"
"693","is waived if you make regular investments weekly, semi-monthly,"
"694","or monthly through automatic deductions through your bank"
"695","checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is waiving the"
"696","minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial investments"
"697","under the minimum."
